page.title: 07Animal feed manufacturer
page.content: Johnsons is a type of factory.It makes food for farm animals. And has been { {established}for{forty eight}years.It has ten lorries in all.There are{forty {six}people employed there.The lorries only travel during the day, usually making two loads a day.The lorries can take either seven to twenty tons of animal feed.Some men work day and night.They make the food from wheat, barley,soyabean,fishmeal,sunflowerseed and maze.They grind it all up and make it into pellets the main ingredient of the pellets are{wheat }and{barley. Other things are added depending on the type of{animal}it is to be fed to.
